    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The family of Taxodiaceae was formerly regarded as a distinct plant family containing ten genera of coniferous trees: Athrotaxis, Cryptomeria, Cunninghamia, Glyptostrobus, Metasequoia, Sciadopitys, Sequoia, Sequoiadendron, Taiwania, and Taxodium. Based on genetic research, it is now generally accepted that all genera except Sciadopitys are actually part of the family Cupressaceae.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000093795/Encyclopedia Britannica Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>De familie Taxodiaceae werd voorheen beschouwd als afzonderlijke plantenfamilie die uit tien genera van kegeldragende bomen bestond: Athrotaxis, Cryptomeria, Cunninghamia, Glyptostrobus, Metasequoia, Sciadopitys, Sequoia, Sequoiadendron, Taiwania en Taxodium. Op basis van genetisch onderzoek wordt nu echter algemeen erkend dat alle genera met uitzondering van Sciadopitys feitelijk tot de familie Cupressaceae behoren.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>杉科曾經被視為一個獨立的植物科別，包含針葉樹的十個屬：密葉杉屬（Athrotaxis）、柳杉屬（Cryptomeria）、杉木屬（Cunninghamia）、水松屬（Glyptostrobus）、水杉屬（Metasequoia）、金松屬（Sciadopitys）、紅杉屬（Sequoia）、巨杉屬（Sequoiadendron）、臺灣杉屬（Taiwania），以及落羽杉屬（Taxodium）。根據基因學的研究，現在公認除了金松屬以外，所有屬別實際上都是柏科的一部分。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
